# App session flows (4 tabs, many scenarios)

## ACTIVE FOCUS ‚Äî Guest (G1) sprint
**All requirements are Guest user flow unless you say otherwise.** Authenticated variants (A1‚ÄìA6) exist as placeholders only ‚Äî do not build them yet.

- Session stays on **`guestUserSession`** (`userSessionProvider` ‚Üí `SessionAuth.guest`).
- Implement in **`*_tab_guest_screen.dart`** + **`data/*_guest_*`** + shared **`widgets/`**.
- Guest Health/Reports = **whole-family multi-user** sample (My Health / Mom / Dad).
- Do not wire login gates, phone verify, or real API session switching unless explicitly requested.
- Keep theme/layout in `core/theme/` + `core/widgets/ds_*` ‚Äî guest work composes those, never forks them.
- **Default tab lists** ‚Üí `DsCategoryStyleList` family (see `.cursor/rules/design-system.mdc` + `docs/design_system.md`).

## Invariant shell
- Tabs: **Tests ¬∑ Reports ¬∑ Health ¬∑ Account** ‚Äî same `AppShell`, same `RoutePaths`, every scenario.
- Theme: only `lib/core/theme/` + `lib/core/widgets/ds_*.dart`. Variants compose design system; no per-flow colors.
- Lists: `DsCategoryStyleList` is the default stacked-row pattern for all tabs (`docs/design_system.md`).

## State model
| Axis | Scope | Values |
|------|-------|--------|
| Auth | account | `guest` ¬∑ `authenticated` |
| Family | account | `none` ¬∑ `members` |
| Phone | account | unverified ¬∑ verified (once per account; gates checkout) |
| Lab data | **per member** | `none` ¬∑ `pending` ¬∑ `available` |

## Locked product decisions
1. **Guest Health/Reports** ‚Äî always multi-user family sample (My Health / Mom / Dad), never single-user.
2. **Pending** ‚Äî one flag **per family member**, not account-wide.
3. **Phone** ‚Äî verify once per account; optional phone on individual members.

## Scenarios
- **G1 Guest** ‚Äî multi-member sample Health/Reports (current Health tab = guest).
- **A1‚ÄìA6** ‚Äî authenticated; derive from per-member lab state + family count.
- **Mixed** ‚Äî common case: some members pending, some with results, some empty.

## File layout per tab
```
features/{tab}/presentation/{tab}_tab_screen.dart
features/{tab}/presentation/variants/{tab}_tab_{scenario}_screen.dart
features/{tab}/presentation/widgets/
features/{tab}/data/
features/session/   # UserSessionContext, FamilyMemberSession, providers
```

## Implemented structure
- `features/session/` ‚Äî domain, `userSessionProvider`, scenario resolvers
- `features/health/` ‚Äî `health_tab_screen.dart` + guest variant + shared widgets
- `features/reports/`, `features/tests/`, `features/account/` ‚Äî tab routers + guest variants
- Router imports only `*TabScreen` entry points, never variants directly.

See `docs/app_session_flows.md` for full architecture.
